Package: BoliviaReadR
Type: Package
Title: Read Public News Content from La Razon Bolivia
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Sana", family = "W.", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "sana@example.com")
)
Description: A lightweight, unofficial client for working with public pages from
    La Razon Bolivia. The package wraps common section pages, headline retrieval,
    article parsing, site-search style queries, and optional WordPress JSON API
    calls when available. It is designed as a practical, transparent scraper for
    reproducible exploratory analysis rather than an official API binding.
